{"tid":1320990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日後想進步就入嚟檢討","createTime":"2019-07-15T14:10:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T11:11:37.000Z","uid":133519,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"07b1a2bb687e07be951cf2cec1cf73a7822bde50","tid":1320990,"uid":133519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:10:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">汪汪方面：</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一、對鞋唔防滑</span><br />\n有幾隻一齊跣到仆街。防線好好利用呢點！波子，番梘水，香蕉皮。<br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">二、少狗時係會淆底</span><br />\n把握機會，打亂佢部署，唔好on99企喺度等狗部署增緩。要記著我哋多人過佢哋。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我哋自己方面：</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一、咪撚亂講嘢</span><br />\n第一，揸大聲公嘅琴晚由七點就開始叫人走，叫到八點幾，喺度擾亂軍心，你係有料先好揸咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n第二，八點幾就傳沙田封站，結果係流料，但係搞到自己驚，又走一批，唔好人講你就傳。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">二、適當時就反守為攻</span><br />\n琴日準備咁多禮物得咁小用到，就係戰略錯咗。狗小就反守為攻，狗多就走去第二度再玩過，<span style=\"color: red;\">咪死守防線，因為我哋都無能力死守，琴日就係死守，俾狗有大量時間部署，如果唔係入到商場，我哋全部已經仆哂街。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">防線雜物係為咗阻住狗，唔係死守。請參考魚蛋革命。<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"345eccacd11aa0b59efb5e81160acea9050de337","tid":1320990,"uid":266036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:13:29.000Z","msg":"油溝水會唔會堅d？ <br />\n人人帶定支，有備無患<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ae88acfade079c6f0aeadb78f3cadf5e1c57d61","tid":1320990,"uid":133519,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"345eccacd11aa0b59efb5e81160acea9050de337","tid":1320990,"uid":266036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:13:29.000Z","msg":"油溝水會唔會堅d？ <br />\n人人帶定支，有備無患<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:16:36.000Z","msg":"啱，一人一枝，用茶樽裝<br />\n<img src=\"https://e.share.photo.xuite.net/lee104t/1e30414/16215436/870059400_m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fe.share.photo.xuite.net%2Flee104t%2F1e30414%2F16215436%2F870059400_m.jpg&h=19712d84&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a05ba58111d7b19b0d8225f44e184b8136235e7b","tid":1320990,"uid":50502,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:17:13.000Z","msg":"有冇人認真分析所謂勇武係想點<br />\n<br />\n一班人出黎唔知有咩守 個個沙包咁企定等狗衝黎打<br />\n開遮唔郁 就好似吉起屎忽等比人屌咁<br />\n衝=帶頭盔食棍/噴霧<br />\n人多時淨係大叫黑警<br />\n沙田贏係因為易走 班狗又保持唔到隊型又出唔到多武器<br />\n金鐘真係極不利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果照用過往示威方法"},{"pid":"e18bbb938477b88ac0cc55063e29763026582b41","tid":1320990,"uid":133519,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:18:11.000Z","msg":"唔好再守，學以前光復，魚蛋周街玩"},{"pid":"d4a1da641d72e91895fb8bfca4324eebb9cf5438","tid":1320990,"uid":133519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:22:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1049bc9edfaf817f976bb095e1f8e213c7fb6f2","tid":1320990,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:28:50.000Z","msg":"［建制議員應總辭］39嘆冷氣逗人工議員拎光環譴責暴力，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">何君堯關鍵缺席</span></span>聯署<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1320529\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1320529</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"390e4a1b5965b95a190aab422632d4e3943c901e","tid":1320990,"uid":133519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:33:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"55987a4023219d6a945866c0fe542aa24ce57b0e","tid":1320990,"uid":133519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:35:48.000Z","msg":"認真post請幫推"},{"pid":"71b9b627c465af851c175360d44b66c830baa63d","tid":1320990,"uid":133519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:39:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"037415ca38bbd50bdf3371ef94c27b60b66fade5","tid":1320990,"uid":36008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco